sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor User as Client (Browser)
    participant Auth as AuthContext (React)
    participant UI as React Component
    participant API as FastAPI Router
    participant AuthMW as JWT Middleware
    participant FFmpeg as FFmpeg Decoder
    participant Engine as Hash Engine
    participant DB as PostgreSQL DB
    
    User->>UI: Upload query media clip
    UI->>Auth: Get Bearer Token
    Auth-->>UI: JWT Token
    UI->>API: POST /api/identify (MultipartForm)
    API->>AuthMW: Verify Token
    AuthMW->>DB: Fetch User Role
    DB-->>AuthMW: Role (Admin/Mod/Viewer)
    AuthMW-->>API: Validated User
    
    API->>FFmpeg: Extract Audio track
    FFmpeg-->>API: .wav file
    API->>Engine: Run Constellation (STFT)
    Engine-->>API: Audio Hashes
    
    API->>DB: SELECT matched hashes (chunked)
    DB-->>API: Audio Matches
    API->>Engine: Compute Temporal Alignment
    Engine-->>API: Audio Confidence Score
    
    alt Audio Confidence > 35%
        API-->>UI: Return Audio Match Result
    else Audio Confidence <= 35%
        API->>FFmpeg: Extract Keyframes
        FFmpeg-->>API: Image Frames
        API->>Engine: Run DCT pHash
        Engine-->>API: 64-bit Hex Hashes
        API->>DB: Query BK-Tree Index (Hamming Dist < 10)
        DB-->>API: Video Matches
        API-->>UI: Return Combined Match Result
    end
    
    UI-->>User: Display Confidence & Logs
